msgid "Import Files"
msgstr "Impor Berkas"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../files.rst:40
msgid ""
"There are many different ways to import media files into an OpenShot "
"project. When a file is imported successfully, it will be automatically "
"selected and scrolled into view (in the **Project Files** panel). Also, if "
"the **Project Files** panel is not currently visible, OpenShot will "
"automatically display the panel."
msgstr ""
"Ada banyak cara berbeda untuk mengimpor berkas media ke dalam proyek "
"OpenShot. Ketika sebuah berkas berhasil diimpor, berkas tersebut akan "
"otomatis dipilih dan digulirkan ke tampilan (di panel **Berkas Proyek**). "
"Selain itu, jika panel **Berkas Proyek** tidak terlihat saat ini, OpenShot "
"akan secara otomatis menampilkan panel tersebut."

