# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../files.rst:64
msgid ""
"You can paste files and clipboard media straight into OpenShot. If you "
"copied one or more files in your file manager, switch to OpenShot and press :"
"kbd:`Ctrl-V` in the **Project Files** panel to add them, just like importing."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat menempel berkas dan media clipboard langsung ke OpenShot. Jika "
"Anda menyalin satu atau lebih berkas di pengelola berkas Anda, beralih ke "
"OpenShot dan tekan :kbd:`Ctrl-V` di panel **Berkas Proyek** untuk "
"menambahkannya, sama seperti mengimpor."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../files.rst:67
msgid ""
"If you copied media **data** (for example, **Copy Image** in a web browser, "
"a pasted frame from another app, or other image/audio/video clipboard data), "
"press :kbd:`Ctrl-V` in OpenShot to create a file for that clipboard content. "
"OpenShot saves a copy in a temporary folder: ``.openshot_qt/clipboard/``. "
"The new file is then added to your project and appears in **Project Files**."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda menyalin data media **(data)** (misalnya, **Salin Gambar** di "
"peramban web, frame yang ditempel dari aplikasi lain, atau data clipboard "
"gambar/audio/video lainnya), tekan :kbd:`Ctrl-V` di OpenShot untuk membuat "
"berkas dari konten clipboard tersebut. OpenShot menyimpan salinan di folder "
"sementara: ``.openshot_qt/clipboard/``. Berkas baru kemudian ditambahkan ke "
"proyek Anda dan muncul di **Berkas Proyek**."

